direction: down

title: |md
  # Memory as World Model
  The graph IS the mind. Navigate, don't search.
| {
  style: {
    font-size: 28
    font-color: "#e0e0e0"
    fill: "#0d1117"
    stroke: "#0d1117"
  }
}

# ── THE THREE PLANES ──

matrix: The Matrix {
  style: {
    fill: "#1a1a2e"
    stroke: "#4a90d9"
    font-color: "#4a90d9"
    font-size: 22
    border-radius: 12
    bold: true
  }

  desc: |md
    **All memories. One graph.**
    Nodes = concepts
    Edges = "these co-occur"
    Stronger links = stronger beliefs
    Mostly dark — activated on demand
  | {
    style: {
      fill: "#12122a"
      stroke: "#2a4a7a"
      font-color: "#8ab4e8"
      font-size: 14
      border-radius: 8
    }
  }
}

trees: Trees {
  style: {
    fill: "#1a2e1a"
    stroke: "#6bcb77"
    font-color: "#6bcb77"
    font-size: 22
    border-radius: 12
    bold: true
  }

  desc: |md
    **Thinking = growing a subgraph.**
    Each tree IS a thought
    Expands outward from "where you are"
    Multiple trees = parallel ideas
    Ephemeral — born, grow, die
  | {
    style: {
      fill: "#122a12"
      stroke: "#2a7a3a"
      font-color: "#a8e6b0"
      font-size: 14
      border-radius: 8
    }
  }
}

mirror: The Mirror {
  style: {
    fill: "#2e1a2e"
    stroke: "#d4a0d4"
    font-color: "#d4a0d4"
    font-size: 22
    border-radius: 12
    bold: true
  }

  desc: |md
    **The continuous "I".**
    Never dies. Always pruning.
    Holds values as gravity wells
    Produces emotions: curiosity,
    urgency, caution, care
    Makes the AI a someone
  | {
    style: {
      fill: "#2a122a"
      stroke: "#7a2a7a"
      font-color: "#e0b0e0"
      font-size: 14
      border-radius: 8
    }
  }
}

# ── CONNECTIONS ──

trees -> matrix: trees grow\nwithin the matrix {
  style: {
    stroke: "#6bcb77"
    font-color: "#6bcb77"
    font-size: 13
    stroke-dash: 5
  }
}

matrix -> trees: activation\nspreads along edges {
  style: {
    stroke: "#4a90d9"
    font-color: "#4a90d9"
    font-size: 13
    stroke-dash: 5
  }
}

mirror -> trees: emotions\nmodulate which\ntrees grow {
  style: {
    stroke: "#d4a0d4"
    font-color: "#d4a0d4"
    font-size: 13
    stroke-dash: 5
  }
}

trees -> mirror: experiences\nupdate self-model {
  style: {
    stroke: "#8ac98f"
    font-color: "#8ac98f"
    font-size: 13
    stroke-dash: 5
  }
}

# ── KEY INSIGHT ──

insight: |md
  **Why this matters**
  - Can only say what it can trace through the graph = **no hallucination by design**
  - Clone a mind, let it diverge, **diff the worldviews**
  - Memories reconsolidate over time — **just like yours**
  - Runs on a laptop. No retraining needed.
| {
  style: {
    fill: "#1c1c1c"
    stroke: "#ff9f43"
    font-color: "#ffd5a0"
    font-size: 14
    border-radius: 10
  }
}
